{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "cc26-psu096-copilot-backend",
    "name": "Coding Camp Copilot — Backend API",
    "description": "REST API untuk Capstone CC26-PSU096 (Coding Camp 2026, DBS Foundation × Dicoding).\n\n**Folder order udah didesain aman untuk Runner sekuensial:**\n1. Health → cek server + DB + AI\n2. Auth → Register + Login Peserta (sets token=peserta)\n3. Chat → semua chat tests pakai token Peserta\n4. Admin → Login Admin (overrides token) + admin tests + Logout cleanup\n5. Error Cases → skenario validasi & auth\n\nScript auto-save `access_token`, `refresh_token`, `current_user_id`, `last_conversation_id`, `last_target_user_id` ke environment.\n\n**Cara pakai (Runner):**\n1. Import collection + environment file\n2. Set environment aktif: `Local Dev`\n3. Pastikan backend jalan (`npm run dev` di folder `RestAPI/`)\n4. Buka Runner → centang semua → Run\n5. Lihat semua test ijo ✅\n\n**Manual mode:** klik request satu-satu dari atas ke bawah, hasilnya sama.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:5001/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "description": "Endpoint monitoring server, database, dan AI service.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 atau 503', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([200, 503]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Response has checks object', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.checks).to.have.property('database');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.checks).to.have.property('ai_service');",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('DB:', json.checks.database, '| AI:', json.checks.ai_service);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Cek status server + ping ke PostgreSQL + ping ke AI service (timeout 3s).\n\nReturn 200 kalau semua ok, 503 kalau ada yang down.\n\n`ai_service` nilai: `ok` atau `down`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Root Info",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:5001/",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "5001",
              "path": [""]
            },
            "description": "App info — nama, versi, link docs."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Auth endpoints — Register + Login Peserta + tests sebagai Peserta.\n\nLogin (Admin) dan Logout sengaja dipindah ke folder **Admin** supaya Runner bisa jalan sekuensial tanpa kehilangan token di tengah.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 atau 409', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([201, 409]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Default role adalah peserta', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.user.role).to.eql('peserta');",
                  "    });",
                  "    console.log('User baru dibuat:', json.data.user.email);",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code === 409) {",
                  "    console.log('User newuser@codingcamp.id sudah ada (OK — dari run sebelumnya)');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"newuser@codingcamp.id\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123\",\n  \"full_name\": \"User Baru\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Daftar user baru `newuser@codingcamp.id` (default role: peserta). Akun ini nanti dipakai sebagai target Update/Delete di folder Admin.\n\nResponse 201 → sukses (first run)\nResponse 409 → email sudah ada (subsequent runs, sebelum Delete dijalanin)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Peserta)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Response has token & user', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.refresh_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Role peserta', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.user.role).to.eql('peserta');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.environment.set('access_token', json.data.token);",
                  "pm.environment.set('refresh_token', json.data.refresh_token);",
                  "pm.environment.set('current_user_id', json.data.user.id);",
                  "pm.environment.set('current_user_email', json.data.user.email);",
                  "pm.environment.set('current_user_role', json.data.user.role);",
                  "console.log('Login PESERTA:', json.data.user.email);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"peserta@codingcamp.id\",\n  \"password\": \"copilot2026\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai peserta (demo account). Token otomatis tersimpan di environment."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Me",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Email match dengan login', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.user.email).to.eql(pm.environment.get('current_user_email'));",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('Current user:', json.data.user.name, '(' + json.data.user.role + ')');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Get info user yang sedang login (dari Bearer token)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Me",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('full_name ter-update', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.user.name).to.eql('Peserta Update Test');",
